<br>
As the woman lifted her head and looked at Hippolyte, she could see the surprise in her eyes.  But, didn't say a word.  Parting her lips, she gently took the food from the woman's fingers.  Hippolyte knew the food was surely not the best, but at the moment it tasted incredible.  She ate each bite offered.  Thankful to have something to eat.  She gave the woman a soft smile.  Then whispered, &quot;What is your name?&quot;<br>
<br>
Then Hipp felt a thud in her battered side that took her breath away.  <br>
<br>
&quot;Don't speak to the slave, Beast!&quot; ordered the guard who had hit her with the blunt end of his sword.<br>
<br>
Hippolyte tried to catch her breath, the pain in her side was just too much now. <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>

"We ride tonight!  With the strength that Hera has given
